Q2. Create the below pattern using nested for loop in Python.
    for i in [1,2,3,4,5]:
        print ('*'*(i)) 
        if i==5: 
        for i in [4,3,2,1]:
            print('*'*(i))
            
Q3. Write a Python program to reverse a word after accepting the input from the user.
    variable1=input()
    variable2=variable1[::-1]
    print(variable2)
    
